I swore an oath to an ideal and a document meant for all people.  I did not enlist, willingly, to watch the American Taliban deny basic.  Human. Rights. To citizens because they somehow believe we were ever a Christian nation. 

This is why I left my church. 
This is why I will take my job and leave the military.
